race.comment: PAW ROXY (6) is a progressive type who recorded her 16th career win last time out (25.15) at Ballarat. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Can make it back-to-back wins. LOVELY LAINEY (2) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 6 lengths back in third (24.18) at Bendigo in a Grade 5 over 425m. Winning chance. PAW CHEYENNE (1) has strong credentials from this draw. Something for the Multiples: GRAB THE GOLD (4)
